Zeus is a character who illustrates Matt Furie in the world of Pepe the Frog. This is evident through Zeus’s distinctive earring, mirroring the one worn by Matt Furie himself.

It has recently come to light that the art of Zeus (Pepe’s Dog) was created by the digital artist ndhaus (@aradew55) on February 7, 2022, as a gift for his supportive friend Jagged (@jaggedsoft).

Ndhaus creatively merges elements from Matt Furie, his art, and Jagged’s real-life dog to craft the character of Zeus. This artistic fusion reflects Ndhaus’s deep admiration for Furie’s distinctive style and Boys Club comics.

Today, Zeus is widely acknowledged within the crypto community as Pepe’s Dog and Matt Furies alter ego. Zeus is a dog that draws a direct connection to Matt. He embodies the large global community that marvels and support the works of Furie.

Zeus, Pepe’s Dog, is the ultimate tribute to the life-changing impact Matt’s work has made on the crypto space and people worldwide. Making Zeus a one-of-a-kind canine and a digital manifestation of Matt Furie himself.

Create a Wallet

Download metamask or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to metamask.io.

 

Get Some ETH

Have ETH in your wallet to swap to $ZEUS. If you don’t have any ETH, you can buy directly on metamask, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to Uniswap

Connect to Uniswap. Go to app.uniswap.org in google chrome or on the browser inside your Metamask app. Connect your wallet. Paste the $ZEUS token address into Uniswap, select ZEUS, and confirm. When Metamask prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

Swap ETH for $ZEUS

Swap ETH for $ZEUS. We have ZERO taxes so you don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.

$ZEUS coin has no association with Matt Furie, Ndhaus or Jaggedsoft. It’s a tribute to the artists and the memes we know and love. $ZEUS is a meme coin without any real value or financial expectations. There’s no formal team or roadmap. It’s all about enjoying the ride.
